description: IntraFreqMCCellProfile: Table storing intra-frequency cell profile parameters for specific cells, including identification, coverage triggers, and configuration details.  dateTime: Timestamp of data recording; Area_Name: Geographic area of the cell; CellId: Unique identifier of the cell; Id2: Duplicate of CellId; Id3: Ancillary identifier (currently '1'); Id4: Ancillary identifier (currently 'Default'); vsDataType: Data type identifier; vsDataFormatVersion: Version of data format; IntraFreqMCCellProfile.userLabel: User-defined label; IntraFreqMCCellProfile.sCellCoverageTriggerQuantity: Trigger quantity for cell coverage (e.g., RSRP); IntraFreqMCCellProfile.rsrpSCellCoverage: Serving cell RSRP threshold; IntraFreqMCCellProfile.rsrqSCellCoverage: Serving cell RSRQ threshold; IntraFreqMCCellProfile.rsrpBetterSCell: RSRP threshold for better serving cell; IntraFreqMCCellProfile.reservedBy: Reserved field; IntraFreqMCCellProfile.ueConfGroupType: UE configuration group type; IntraFreqMCCellProfile.intraFreqMCCellProfileId: Identifier for the intra-frequency cell profile.
